{"tid":1543902,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"關心下未成年要入兒童院嘅手足","createTime":"2019-09-05T11:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T11:10:35.000Z","uid":310846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b27a237abfdef63a3a9cc87db2bf8027f29dd3bb","tid":1543902,"uid":310846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:08:15.000Z","msg":"入左去真係俾人打死都唔知呀<br />\n<br />\n15歲中學男生於8月29日晚上出席深水埗放映會後被捕，上周六（8月31日）與另兩名中學生遭警方申請保護令而被帶上少年庭，被裁判官判入兒童院暫住，以待索取社署報告，案件9月27日再訊。該名男生的家人早前入稟高院申請人身保護令及司法覆核。法官今午（5日）宣布人身保護令押後爭拗，但批准司法覆核的許可申請，容許男生即日起暫時釋放，直至9月27日提堂為止，其間不得參與非法活動；法官另要求男生須每晚10時至早上6時遵守宵禁令。<br />\n<br />\n警方上周六為3名被捕中學生向法庭申請保護令，是兩個多月反修例衝突中的首次。15歲男生的家人日前向高院提出覆核及申請人身保護令，要求立即釋放男生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190905/s00001/1567674985782\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190905%2Fs00001%2F1567674985782&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MB3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=87003001\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190905%2Fs00001%2F1567674985782&h=ac3ff43a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190905/s00001/1567674985782</a>"},{"pid":"cd2cbf2e0fafb6e43cca0f9d16077896b48e750c","tid":1543902,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:10:35.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 出咗不反對啦！【9月6 反濫捕 抗威權 遮打集會】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543083</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂]9.6遮打反濫暴抗威權集會 已獲批不反對通知書<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/agyFBwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/agyFBwU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTsuWvi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTsuWvi.jpg&h=59781468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https: